==Phagocytosis==
[[Phagocyte]]s are [[cell (biology)|cells]] that can perform [[phagocytosis]] of inorganic or organic (including other cells and [[pathogen]]s) material. Phagocytes include the [[macrophage]] and the [[neutrophil granulocyte]].

